<item>
            <title>[CXF-6679]  @Context HttpServletRequest request.getParameterMap() can&apos;t contain post parameters by application/x-www-form-urlencoded</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CXF-6679</link>
                <project id="12310511" key="CXF">CXF</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;	@POST&lt;br/&gt;
	@Path(&quot;/post&quot;)&lt;br/&gt;
	public String post( @Context HttpServletRequest request )&lt;/p&gt;
{
		Map&amp;lt;String, String[]&amp;gt; reMap = request.getParameterMap();
		System.out.println( reMap );
		return reMap.toString();
	}
&lt;p&gt;In reMap, there are no post parameters.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
